    "The second season begins in October 1984, as we see a teenage girl with psychic powers and the number 008 tattooed on her arm rob a bank in Pittsburgh.Meanwhile, over in Hawkins, the boys meet new girl Max (Sadie Sink) at school.Her arrival isn\’t the only change in Hawkins. Joyce is dating her former school classmate Bob (Sean Astin), while her son Will has been experiencing visions of the Upside Down and a shadowy monster.Joyce and Hopper take him to see the Hawkins\’ lab\’s new director, Dr Owens (Paul Reiser), who is regularly studying Will when he isn\’t worrying that the gate in the lab\’s basement seems to be getting bigger (ruh-roh!).";
